S.FORM: = Rʉhlʉcʉ/Haising = Gaga mniq Kawsyungsu Tawyuncyu ka alang Rʉhlʉcʉ/Haising. 169 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 574 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 91% niqan 521 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 9% niqan 53 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Bunun65%, Rukai1%, Cou5%, Paiwan 6%, Hla'alua 11%, Amis 2%, ni rahuq na o 1%.
